## 🔍 Introduction
The Thief Video Classifier uses advanced preprocessing techniques to analyze video files and identify suspicious behavior. This tool is designed for security applications.

## ⚙️ Features
- 📹 Processes video files
- 🚨 Outputs whether a thief is detected

### 📋 Prerequisites
- Python 3.7+
- OpenCV
- TensorFlow/Keras
- NumPy
